questions.quote: Aww, man. That's the girl I was hiding from. When she finds out he's my roommate, she's gonna tell him what I did.

I don't know! What could she possibly be hiding in here that I can't see?!
No, wait. No there's gotta be something else that you can do. I mean, what skills do you have?
Hey. Rachel, I-I-I've been wanting to tell you something for a while now and I really, I just have to get it out.
